OL,3,CVictims speak of 'traumatic' car crash
OL,4,Cmemories as drink-driver jailed
OL,6,FA 31-year-old drink driver who
OL,7,Fseriously injured three people,
OL,8,Fincluding a child, has been jailed.
OL,10,FSamuel Staynings crashed head-on with
OL,11,Fanother car on Brunel Way in Bristol
OL,12,Fin November 2022.
OL,14,FInside the other car was married
OL,15,Fcouple Chris and Jennie Owen and a
OL,16,Fyoung boy - all of whom suffered
OL,17,F'significant injuries'.
