OL,3,CVictims speak of 'traumatic' car crash
OL,4,Cmemories as drink-driver jailed
OL,6,FThe crash happened after the 31-year-
OL,7,Fold failed to change lanes when the
OL,8,Fdual carriageway section merged into
OL,9,Fone.
OL,11,FThe couple describe still being
OL,12,F'haunted' by the events that unfolded
OL,13,Fthat day.
OL,15,FChris, 50, sustained fractures to his
OL,16,Fneck, leg, knee and wrist while
OL,17,FJennie, 55, suffered fractures to her
OL,18,Fwrist, hand and feet. The boy
OL,19,Fsustained abdominal injuries as well
OL,20,Fas a fractured vertebra.
