OL,3,CVictims speak of 'traumatic' car crash
OL,4,Cmemories as drink-driver jailed
OL,6,FIn a statement, Jennie wrote how the
OL,7,Fscene she witnessed continues to haunt
OL,8,Fher.
OL,10,FShe also described being distraught
OL,11,Fwhen finding out her wedding ring had
OL,12,Fto be cut off due to the fractures on
OL,13,Fher hand.
OL,15,FShe also spoke of her pain at being
OL,16,Fseparated from her husband while he
OL,17,Freceived treatment for his injuries
OL,18,Fand of becoming his carer overnight.
