OL,3,CVictims speak of 'traumatic' car crash
OL,4,Cmemories as drink-driver jailed
OL,6,F"To have to watch my husband struggle
OL,7,Fevery day with daily life is very
OL,8,Ftraumatic," she said.
OL,10,F"I find it extremely difficult to come
OL,11,Fto terms with as this situation could
OL,12,Fhave been avoided."
OL,14,FIn addition to his prison sentence,
OL,15,FStaynings has also been banned from
OL,16,Fdriving for seven and a half years.
