OL,3,CVictims speak of 'traumatic' car crash
OL,4,Cmemories as drink-driver jailed
OL,6,FSergeant Matt Boiles said: "Samuel
OL,7,FStaynings' decision to get behind the
OL,8,Fwheel of his car when he knew he had
OL,9,Fdrunk too much alcohol has had
OL,10,Fdevastating consequences.
OL,12,F"A family's whole way of life has been
OL,13,Fchanged forever. He will now spend a
OL,14,Fsignificant amount of time behind bars
OL,15,Fand I hope he reflects on what
OL,16,Fhappened and never makes the same
OL,17,Fmistake again.
